= SMEMBERS _key_ =
_Time complexity O(N)_

 Return all the members (elements) of the set value stored at _key_. This
 is just syntax glue for [SintersectCommand SINTERSECT].

== Return value ==

[ReplyTypes Multi bulk reply]
